data.description: If you are looking for a top-notch construction in a family-friendly resort, you will love this gorgeous 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home at Harrison's Walk, just down the street from the County Pier. This home features an additional ''flex'' space that would make a perfect office or play area, as well as a gas fireplace, a tankless water heater, a pex plumbing manifold, and a metal roof.This home has a beautiful and spacious floor plan, with travertine and hardwood floors, crown molding, custom cabinets, and granite countertops. The master bedroom is on the main level, and the other three bedrooms are upstairs. The home also has a large, covered front porch where you can enjoy the weather and the neighborhood. The home comes with high-speed internet, cable TV, and a washer and dryer.The Harrison's Walk community offers you a variety of amenities and facilities to make your stay enjoyable and memorable. You can relax by the large community pool, or visit the nearby attractions and restaurants. You can easily access the Pier Park, the ZooWorld, the Gulf World Marine Park, and the Shipwreck Island Waterpark. You can also sample the local cuisine at the nearby eateries, such as the Saltwater Grill, the Firefly, and the Pineapple Willy's.The best part is that this home has an assumable loan. Don't miss this opportunity to own a stunning and comfortable home in one of the most beautiful beach destinations in Florida. Contact us today and make your dream come true!
